---
// src/pages/about.astro
import BaseHead from '../components/BaseHead.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
---
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <BaseHead
      title="About Deskbly"
      description="Deskbly is a home office blog sharing ergonomic tips, honest gear reviews, and setup guides to help you work comfortably from home."
    />
    <style>
      .page { max-width: 720px; margin: 3rem auto; padding: 0 1.5rem; }
      h1 { font-size: 2rem; font-weight: 800; color: #111; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; }
      .subtitle { color: #666; font-size: 1.1rem; margin-bottom: 2rem; }
      p { line-height: 1.8; color: #444; margin-bottom: 1.25rem; }
      h2 { font-size: 1.3rem; font-weight: 700; color: #111; margin-top: 2rem; }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <Header />
    <main class="page">
      <h1>About Deskbly</h1>
      <p class="subtitle">Your guide to a healthier, more comfortable home office.</p>

      <p>
        Deskbly was created for people who spend long hours working from home and want to do it without wrecking their back, neck, or wrists. We cover everything from ergonomic chair recommendations to cable management tips — practical advice you can actually use.
      </p>

      <h2>What we cover</h2>
      <p>
        Every article on Deskbly is focused on one thing: helping you build a home office that works for your body. That means honest gear reviews, step-by-step setup guides, and tips backed by ergonomic principles — not just what looks good on a desk tour.
      </p>

      <h2>Affiliate disclosure</h2>
      <p>
        Some articles on Deskbly contain affiliate links, meaning we may earn a small commission if you buy through them — at no extra cost to you. This helps keep the site running. We only recommend products we genuinely believe in. See our full <a href="/disclaimer/">disclaimer here</a>.
      </p>

      <h2>Get in touch</h2>
      <p>
        Have a question, topic suggestion, or just want to say hi? <a href="/contact/">Contact us here.</a>
      </p>
    </main>
    <Footer />
  </body>
</html>
